Package: swecris
Title: SweCRIS - Grant Decisions From Swedish Funding Bodies And
    EU
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Markus",
           family = "Skyttner",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "markussk@kth.se")
Description: SweCRIS is a national database that allows you to
    see how participating research funding bodies has distributed their
    money to Swedish recipients. The research funding bodies which supply
    SweCRIS with data are either state or private. Contributions are
    divided according to grant contracts. SweCRIS is managed by the
    Swedish Research Council on behalf of the Government. This R package
    uses the open API at SweCRIS to make data available for use from R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/KTH-Library/swecris
BugReports: https://github.com/KTH-Library/swecris/issues
